class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1de74a2c16fb9f06a7887c1a29f648625dafcf","tid":1537644,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04621e5b2ed7fcf6f5bc441a63eb376edb91fa44","tid":1537644,"uid":291405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T18:54:55.000Z","msg":"8.31太子傳死訊 戰友報平安<br />\n(沒有事? 我懷疑受訪者認錯人﹐當了另一人是在地上沒有知覺那位)<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網上盛傳8.31於太子站月台被速龍警員按倒地上施襲、懷疑失去知覺的男子已經死亡，但同在當晚被捕的阿俊（化名）向《蘋果》表示，在扣查時曾與該男子傾談，有講有笑，無見到他有明顯傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n當中就有《蘋果》當日直播影片中被兩名速龍警員按倒在地上、再用警棍攻擊的男子，「出返嚟先知網上話佢死咗，嗰晚有同佢傾過幾句，平安嘅，行得走得，唔覺有咩明顯傷，仲有講有笑」。但他未有留意該男子幾時離開警署，「係保釋定送去第二度真係唔知」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190905/20762561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762561&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3KQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=0df133b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762561&h=ec43f756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190905/20762561</a><br />\n~~~"}]}